    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tf_block_details",
      "x": 1270, "y": 1050,
      "width": 410, "height": 150,
      "text": "Each block:\n  1. Intra-band LSTM → local frequency structure\n  2. Inter-frame LSTM → temporal context\n     (causal, h/c state persists across chunks)\n  3. Local causal attention\n     4 heads, window 50\n     K/V buffers persist across chunks\n\n  Speaker embedding injected at Block 2",
      "originalText": "Each block:\n  1. Intra-band LSTM → local frequency structure\n  2. Inter-frame LSTM → temporal context\n     (causal, h/c state persists across chunks)\n  3. Local causal attention\n     4 heads, window 50\n     K/V buffers persist across chunks\n\n  Speaker embedding injected at Block 2",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
